org.rapidcontext.util

Class HttpUtil.STATUS

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.rapidcontext.util.HttpUtil.STATUS
  • Enclosing interface:
    HttpUtil

    public abstract static class HttpUtil.STATUS
extends java.lang.Object
    The HTTP status codes as defined in RFC1945 (HTTP/1.0), RFC2616 (HTTP/1.1), and RFC4918 (WebDAV).
